\b0 Several scripts and behaviors can be mixed to obtain a unique and special destruction behaviour. To achieve this without any unnecessary effort, a set of example prefabs come with this package. The specific behaviour of each prefab is often referred to using a set of simple letters, that will immediately tell you which group of CPs each one of them belongs to.\
