- mm		amm		Mesh modifier only, doesn't affect colliders.\
- cm		acm		Collider modifier, doesn't affect the mesh itself.\
- tm 		atm		Texture modifier, only changes texture/UV/bumps or any shader settings.\
- um		umm		Updating modifier, continuously modifies the CP.\
